examples.en: The beats in this joint were the bomb!
The husband drinks and beats his wife.
Triple time has three beats per measure.
Fresh milk beats powdered milk any time.
The average person's heart beats 70 times a minute.
'Well,' said Culley, 'it beats going to the office.'
He beats his children for even the smallest misdemeanour.
You are not the kind of person who beats on recalcitrant vending machines.
It beats all / anything / creation / the world / the band / hell / the devil / my grandmother.
